{
  "texts": [
    "There are a growing number of APIs in the field of AI that allow developers and companies to easily access AI systems and integrate them into their applications.",
    "For example, an e-commerce company can use APIs to offer customized recommendations and a personalized shopping experience to its customers, increasing purchase conversion (Medium.com 2023c).",
    "These skills and approaches can help companies take advantage of the opportunities offered by AI and large language models.",
    "AI is an increasingly widespread technology, and those who properly prepare and apply it can gain a competitive advantage in the age of digitization and automation.",
    "Large language models can have a significant impact on economic growth and competitiveness, but it is important to note that this impact depends on many factors and is not always clear-cut or exclusively positive."
  ]
}